extends layout

block content
  div(class='card')
    div(class='card-content')
      h4 🙇 Sorry! 🙏
      p We are so sorry but currently only a limited number of testers will be allowed to use Maarfapad.
      br
      p We really appreciate your interest and would really, really want you to stick around until
      p Maarfapad is fully tested out and ready to receive you.
      br
      p Please follow one of our social media outlets to get
      p notified as soon as we exit testing and are ready to create a home for you and your ideas!
      br
      p Follow Maarfapad via:
    div(class='card-action')
      a(class='waves-effect waves-black btn-flat' href='http://twitter.com/maarfapad')
        span(class='black-text') Twitter
      |  &nbsp  
      a(class='waves-effect waves-black btn-flat' href='http://facebook.com/maarfapad') 
        span(class='black-text') Facebook
      |  &nbsp  
      a(class='waves-effect waves-black btn-flat' href='http://instagram.com/maarfapad')
        span(class='black-text') Instagram
  a(class='waves-effect waves-black btn-flat' href='/') Home